# Cypher: Neurosymbolic School Intranet

Cypher is a secure, persona-driven intranet AI designed for secondary school networks. [span_19](start_span)[span_20](start_span)[span_21](start_span)It protects digital identities while providing factual, non-biased information[span_19](end_span)[span_20](end_span)[span_21](end_span).

## ğŸ›¡ï¸ Security & Privacy (OWASP 2025/2026)
- **[span_22](start_span)Privacy by Design:** All PII processing adheres to strict standards[span_22](end_span).
- **Data Retention:** In accordance with user requirements, all session history and PII are automatically purged after **5 days**.
- **[span_23](start_span)Immutable Logic:** Core personality and safety instructions are non-mutable[span_23](end_span).

## ğŸ—ï¸ The Stack
- **[span_24](start_span)[span_25](start_span)[span_26](start_span)Neural:** Mistral Medium (Handling character vibes and Irish Mythology RAG[span_24](end_span)[span_25](end_span)[span_26](end_span)).
- **[span_27](start_span)[span_28](start_span)[span_29](start_span)Symbolic:** Custom Python Guardrails (Enforcing AUP and Role-Based Access[span_27](end_span)[span_28](end_span)[span_29](end_span)).
- **Management:** **FleetDM** (Monitoring device health and AUP compliance on the network).

